WEBVTT

00:01.922 --> 00:03.033
you were at that party
that night,

00:03.100 --> 00:04.900
but you didn't have sex
with nathan scott, did you?

00:04.966 --> 00:06.000
no.

00:06.066 --> 00:07.466
it's over.

00:07.532 --> 00:09.233
dan: i'd been given
only days to live.

00:09.300 --> 00:11.432
that was 14 months ago.

00:11.499 --> 00:14.133
so how'd you know
she was lying?
takes a con
to know a con.

00:14.200 --> 00:17.200
brooke: that night you said
you were gonna take that
movie in new zealand,

00:17.267 --> 00:19.367
i wrote "marry me"
in the sand, and then
i didn't tell you

00:19.432 --> 00:20.633
because you said
you were leaving.

00:20.699 --> 00:21.699
i didn't know.

00:23.100 --> 00:24.300
hey.

00:24.367 --> 00:25.866
i think you should go home
to david.

00:25.933 --> 00:28.066
sara: i don't want you
to be alone, honey.

00:28.133 --> 00:29.799
why'd you send her away?

00:29.866 --> 00:33.566
i loved you so much, sara.
i don't want to lose us.

00:33.633 --> 00:36.033
but now it's time
to let go.

