my dad will do it.

37:15.200 --> 37:16.866
what?
no. no.

37:16.933 --> 37:19.200
no way i'm going out there, man.
i'm way too scared.

37:22.666 --> 37:24.899
all right.
i'll go.

38:10.666 --> 38:12.666
hey, guys,
it's not drag-leg laura.

38:12.732 --> 38:14.433
it's just some
stupid old gate.

38:19.467 --> 38:22.433
wow, jamie.
that was awesome.

38:22.500 --> 38:25.233
jamie scott --
one bravery badge.

38:25.300 --> 38:27.333
yes.

38:27.400 --> 38:29.799
chuck, you might want to go
change your underwear again.

38:32.166 --> 38:33.766
all right, buddy.

38:37.766 --> 38:40.300
okay.

38:40.366 --> 38:42.732
if this is our last night on
earth, i just want you to know

38:42.799 --> 38:44.866
that i am really glad
we are spending it together.

38:44.933 --> 38:46.433
no, this is silly.
you are just paranoid.

38:46.500 --> 38:48.433
we weren't even hearing things.
it was just the brownies.

38:51.966 --> 38:53.599
it's coming
from the closet.

38:58.033 --> 38:59.500
whew.

39:01.233 --> 39:04.133
this is ridiculous.

39:04.200 --> 39:06.300
cuniculus.

39:06.366 --> 39:07.500
what?

39:07.567 --> 39:08.632
oryctolagus...

39:08.699 --> 39:09.632
cuniculus!cuniculus!

39:10.830 --> 39:12.632
that's what zelda said.

39:12.699 --> 39:18.057
the evil spirit...
in the closet.

39:19.366 --> 39:20.467
here i come.

39:22.300 --> 39:24.133
wait!

39:24.200 --> 39:26.500
oryctolagus cuniculus --

39:26.567 --> 39:28.100
the latin word

39:28.166 --> 39:29.899
for "bunny rabbit."

39:31.333 --> 39:34.666
that zelda's a bitch.

39:36.033 --> 39:39.599
kids are finally back asleep.

39:42.166 --> 39:44.200
how'd you know
about the creaky gate?

39:44.266 --> 39:47.166
oh, i--i just saw it
when i was out getting firewood.

39:49.100 --> 39:51.166
nice performance.

39:51.233 --> 39:53.966
julian.

39:54.033 --> 39:56.500
you knew
jamie needed that.

39:56.567 --> 39:59.066
oh, it was no big deal.

39:59.133 --> 40:01.400
hey, being a father
is 95% instinct.

40:01.467 --> 40:02.866
and you have good ones.

40:04.400 --> 40:06.333
when the day comes,
you'll be ready.

40:07.699 --> 40:09.133
thanks, man.

40:13.699 --> 40:17.166
you know, that was
my first-ever fist bump.

40:17.233 --> 40:18.699
don't overthink it.

40:27.166 --> 40:30.666
come back to bed, baby.
you need rest.

40:30.732 --> 40:34.467
you're right.
i do.

40:34.533 --> 40:36.899
in fact,
i've been thinking.

40:36.966 --> 40:38.999
maybe we need
a vacation.

40:40.899 --> 40:42.500
now, that's my boy.

40:42.567 --> 40:47.699
where do you want to go --
the bahamas, hawaii?

40:49.732 --> 40:51.400
tree hill.

40:51.467 --> 40:53.333
i want to go home.

40:55.666 --> 40:58.500
it's almost morning.
i should go.

41:00.433 --> 41:04.100
or, uh, you could stay.

41:11.500 --> 41:13.833
tell me more about sara.

41:15.866 --> 41:18.033
she would've
really liked you.

